SchemaBuilder
public static final class SchemaBuilder.MapBuilder<R> extends SchemaBuilder.PropBuilder<SchemaBuilder.MapBuilder<R>>
Builds an Avro Map type with optional properties.

Set properties with SchemaBuilder.PropBuilder.prop(String, String).

The Map schema's properties are finalized when values() or values(Schema) is called.
